berg, Brown, Armstrong, and their respective colleagues will play out in board rooms and courtrooms, not to mention the living rooms where so many grassroots sports decisions are made.\", \"from\": 7481, \"to\": 7704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The value\", \"from\": 7481, \"to\": 7490}, {\"ngram\": \"studies\", \"from\": 7494, \"to\": 7501}, {\"ngram\": \"Lundberg\", \"from\": 7516, \"to\": 7524}, {\"ngram\": \"Brown\", \"from\": 7526, \"to\": 7531}, {\"ngram\": \"Armstrong\", \"from\": 7533, \"to\": 7542}, {\"ngram\": \"their respective colleagues\", \"from\": 7548, \"to\": 7575}, {\"ngram\": \"board rooms\", \"from\": 7593, \"to\": 7604}, {\"ngram\": \"courtrooms\", \"from\": 7609, \"to\": 7619}, {\"ngram\": \"the living rooms\", \"from\": 7636, \"to\": 7652}, {\"ngram\": \"so many grassroots sports decisions\", \"from\": 7659, \"to\": 7694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The more decision-makers can rely on research rather than earnest but shallow plaints of \\\"But it's obvious!\\\"\", \"from\": 7705, \"to\": 7813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The more decision-makers\", \"from\": 7705, \"to\": 7729}, {\"ngram\": \"research\", \"from\": 7742, \"to\": 7750}, {\"ngram\": \"earnest but shallow plaints\", \"from\": 7763, \"to\": 7790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"the more women and girls will flourish in fair and competitive sports.\", \"from\": 7814, \"to\": 7884, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the more women\", \"from\": 7814, \"to\": 7828}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 7833, \"to\": 7838}, {\"ngram\": \"fair and competitive sports\", \"from\": 7856, \"to\": 7883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2026 The Federalist, A wholly independent division of FDRLST Media.\", \"from\": 7886, \"to\": 7955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a9\", \"from\": 7886, \"to\": 7887}, {\"ngram\": \"The Federalist\", \"from\": 7893, \"to\": 7907}, {\"ngram\": \"A wholly independent division\", \"from\": 7909, \"to\": 